title: SC EP:105 Throwback Part 2
itunes:title: SC EP:105 Throwback Part 2
description: In part two of the "Throwback" series, Woody and I sit down and talk about past show including "The Spottsville Monster", "Ape Canyon," "Deathbed Confessions," and others. We will also be talking about behind-the-scenes stuff you never got to hear. I hope everyone enjoys the conclusion of the "Throwback" series.
